description:
.NET polyfill to the future. A versatile RAD (Rapid Application Development) framework for .NET platform.

Gapotchenko.FX closes the gaps in original .NET design by providing the long-missing functionality that should have been mainstream since 2012.

This package represents the Core profile of Gapotchenko.FX.

Hint: instead of referencing each individual Gapotchenko.FX module, you can opt-in into referencing a profile.

Commonly Used Modules:
- Gapotchenko.FX
- Gapotchenko.FX.Linq
- Gapotchenko.FX.IO
- Gapotchenko.FX.Diagnostics.WebBrowser
- Gapotchenko.FX.Diagnostics.CommandLine
- Gapotchenko.FX.Threading

Supported Platforms:
- .NET 5.0+
- .NET Standard 2.0+
- .NET Core 2.0+
- .NET Framework 4.5+
